0w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1777675450081_nn_cku_troops_germany_260501_S3_1920x1080-rqr13k.jpg"></media:thumbnail><media:description type="plain">The Pentagon will withdraw roughly 5,000 U.S. troops from Germany, a move that comes amid President Trump’s growing clash with European allies over Iran and NATO tensions. NBC News’ Courtney Kube reports.</media:description><media:subTitle type="text/srt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1777675450081_nn_cku_troops_germany_260501.srt"></media:subTitle><media:subTitle type="text/vtt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1777675450081_nn_cku_troops_germany_260501.vtt"></media:subTitle></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1777675450081_nn_cku_troops_germany_260501_S3_1920x1080-rqr13k.jpg"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 22:44:16 GMT</pubDate><title>Trump administration to pull 5,000 troops from Germany</title><updateDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 23:15:42 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Steve Kopack</dc:creator><dc:contributor>Ryan Beckler</dc:contributor><dc:contributor>Ryan Nobles</dc:contributor><dc:contributor>Monica Alba</dc:contributor><dateTimeWritten>Fri, 01 May 2026 14:22:39 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>The national average gas price rose to $4.39 per gallon, in its biggest one-day jump since a ceasefire with Iran was announced on April 7.</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/business/energy/gas-prices-iran-war-oil-ceasefire-rcna343053</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/business/energy/gas-prices-iran-war-oil-ceasefire-rcna343053</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260501-gas-pumps-gk-577e64.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Patrick T. Fallon</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Image: Vehicles sit parked at fuel pumps as regular gasoline prices above $6 per gallon and diesel prices above $7 per gallon are displayed outside a Mobil gas station </media:text><media:description type="plain">Vehicles sit parked at fuel pumps as regular gasoline prices above $6 per gallon and diesel prices above $7 per gallon are displayed outside a Mobil gas station in Redondo Beach, California on April 30, 2026. Energy costs have surged since the near-total closure of the Strait of Hormuz, through which about a fifth of the world&#39;s oil and gas usually passes, following the outbreak of the US-Israeli war against Iran.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260501-gas-pumps-gk-577e64.jpg" height="1667" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 14:22:39 GMT</pubDate><title>Gas prices hit $4.39 per gallon in biggest one-day jump since Iran ceasefire announced</title><updateDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 22:14:36 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dateTimeWritten>Fri, 01 May 2026 22:48:59 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>The budget airline could abruptly halt all operations in just a few hours. The complete collapse of Spirit would be a huge blow to the airline industry and a major headache for people planning to travel with the carrier in the coming months. NBC News’ Brian Cheung has the latest.</description><expires>2056-05-01T22:48:29.000+0000</expires><guid isPermaLink="false">nn_bch_spirit_airlines_260501</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/nightly-news/video/spirit-airlines-could-shut-down-by-saturday-262565957616</link><media:content url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nn_bch_spirit_airlines_260501/1/abs/index.m3u8" medium="video"><media:credit></media:credit><media:title>Spirit Airlines could shut down by Saturday</media:title><media:player url="https://www.nbcnews.com/nightly-news/video/spirit-airlines-could-shut-down-by-saturday-262565957616"></media:player><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1777675697936_nn_bch_spirit_airlines_260501_S3_1920x1080-1s3wuz.jpg"></media:thumbnail><media:description type="plain">The budget airline could abruptly halt all operations in just a few hours. The complete collapse of Spirit would be a huge blow to the airline industry and a major headache for people planning to travel with the carrier in the coming months. NBC News’ Brian Cheung has the latest.</media:description><media:subTitle type="text/srt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1777675697936_nn_bch_spirit_airlines_260501.srt"></media:subTitle><media:subTitle type="text/vtt" lang="en-US" url="https://prodamdnewsencoding.akamaized.net/NBC_News_Digital/nbcnews/captions/2026/05/1777675697936_nn_bch_spirit_airlines_260501.vtt"></media:subTitle></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/mpx/2704722219/2026_05/1777675697936_nn_bch_spirit_airlines_260501_S3_1920x1080-1s3wuz.jpg"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 22:48:24 GMT</pubDate><title>Spirit Airlines could shut down by Saturday</title><updateDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 22:48:59 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dateTimeWritten>Fri, 01 May 2026 22:51:27 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>A federal appeals court has ruled that the abortion drug mifepristone cannot be sent to patients by mail. Telehealth prescriptions have been key to maintaining abortion access in states that outlawed or restricted the practice after the Supreme Court overturned Roe v. Wade in 2022.</description><expires>2056-05-01T22:50:36.000+0000</expires><guid isPermaLink="false">now_hallie_abortion_pills_mail_260501</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/video/federal-appeals-court-rules-that-abortion-drugs-cannot-be-sent-by-mail-262565957619<